    "notes": "Ⓒ 2015 Sony Music Entertainment / Ⓟ 1990, 1991, 1992, 1993, 1995, 1997, 1999, 2000 Columbia Records,\n2005, 2008 The Island Def Jam Music Group and Mariah Carey, 2015 Epic Records.\n\nA1, A2, A4: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Mariah-Carey/master/78748]Mariah Carey[/url] Ⓟ1990\nA3: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-MTV-Unplugged-EP/master/78765]MTV Unplugged EP[/url] Ⓟ1992. Original version appears on [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Mariah-Carey/master/78748]Mariah Carey[/url]\nA5: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Emotions/master/78076]Emotions[/url] Ⓟ1991\nB1: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-MTV-Unplugged-EP/master/78765]MTV Unplugged EP[/url] Ⓟ1992\nB2, B3: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Music-Box/master/79031]Music Box[/url] Ⓟ1993\nB4: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Fantasy/release/145658]CD Maxi Single[/url] Ⓟ1995. Original version appears on [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Daydream/master/78027]Daydream[/url]\nB5, C1: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Daydream/master/78027]Daydream[/url] Ⓟ1995\nC2, C3: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Butterfly/master/78000]Butterfly[/url] Ⓟ1997\nC4, C5: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-Rainbow/master/78855]Rainbow[/url] Ⓟ1999\nD1, D2: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-The-Emancipation-Of-Mimi/master/78958]The Emancipation Of Mimi[/url] Ⓟ2005\nD3: Taken from [url=http://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-EMC²/master/78066]E=MC[/url] Ⓟ2008\nD4: Exclusive to this collection Ⓟ2015\n\nTrack D4 mastered at 'Powers Mastering, Florida'. \n\n180-gram vinyl in a gatefold release, with a black hype sticker. \nIncludes high-quality MP3 dowloads.\n\nA, B, C & D runouts are etched, 'Welcome to 1979' stamped.",
